[COVID-19 will only exacerbate what is already a very difficult situation for vulnerable communities in the DR Congo where a low immunization rate is exacerbated by malnutrition, weak public health system, outbreaks of other epidemic-prone diseases, difficult access by vulnerable populations to health care and insecurity, as stated by WHO. - Mod.LK]

